{"tid":557880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀之所以印象深刻","createTime":"2018-02-11T17:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T18:35:00.000Z","uid":21212,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48fb8ca6836fe049f8e7921febd7da63d8db9bac","tid":557880,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"係因為你第一次拍拖 <br />\n所以不顧一切付出所有去愛一個人<br />\n希望可以永遠留得住佢 <br />\n<br />\n曾經你地一齊計劃過將來<br />\n曾經你以為可以一齊奮鬥 <br />\n將來睇落係幾咁美好<br />\n<br />\n到最後 佢都係離開左你<br />\n而呢啲夢想 永遠都唔會成真<br />\n你地曾經既美好回憶 <br />\n呢一刻更加成為左你喊既原因<br />\n<br />\n而亦因為初戀傷得太深<br />\n第二次拍拖唔會再敢咁投入<br />\n倒不如留返啲餘地比自己<br />\n好比自己更容易抽離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93db939f35272f8e61e572a9164ab248856159ef","tid":557880,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967fafa8183e2e4836e39f61c54f97412e194150","tid":557880,"uid":130375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:59:58.000Z","msg":"初戀其實唔難忘記，只係初戀既感覺係最真<br />\n利申：初戀一齊接近一年，好返用左一年幾"},{"pid":"e0eb1a68662c06c145449546eca8da2209019020","tid":557880,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"967fafa8183e2e4836e39f61c54f97412e194150","tid":557880,"uid":130375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:59:58.000Z","msg":"初戀其實唔難忘記，只係初戀既感覺係最真<br />\n利申：初戀一齊接近一年，好返用左一年幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"當你第二次拍拖既時候 總係好似有好多其他野要考慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba75ad2dc68b5d2725982e31610cdf5d5a62bc01","tid":557880,"uid":130375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0eb1a68662c06c145449546eca8da2209019020","tid":557880,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"967fafa8183e2e4836e39f61c54f97412e194150","tid":557880,"uid":130375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep